Program: Discovery
Title: New Frontiers in Science
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrw7t
Last Broadcast Date: 20 June 1994
Report from the New Frontiers in Science exhibition at Royal Society in central London. Includes breakthrough imaging technology in brain surgery, news from the electron-proton collider HERA in Hamburg, and experiments you can do at home with tin foil.